#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:61
msgid ""
"As X and Y coordinates (DMS (dd mm ss.ss), DD (dd.dd) or projected "
"coordinates (mmmm.mm)), which correspond with the selected point on the "
"image, two alternative procedures can be used:"
msgstr ""
"Kao X i Y koordinate (DMS (dd mm ss.ss), DD (dd.dd) ili projektovane "
"koordinate (mmmm.mm)), koje odgovaraju izabranoj tački na slici, mogu se "
"koristiti dva alternativna postupka:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:65
msgid ""
"The raster itself sometimes provides crosses with coordinates \"written\" on"
" the image. In this case, you can enter the coordinates manually."
msgstr ""
"Sam raster ponekad pruža krstove sa koordinatama „upisanim“ na slici. U tom "
"slučaju možete ručno uneti koordinate."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:67
msgid ""
"Using already georeferenced layers. This can be either vector or raster data"
" that contain the same objects/features that you have on the image that you "
"want to georeference and with the projection that you want for your image. "
"In this case, you can enter the coordinates by clicking on the reference "
"dataset loaded in the QGIS map canvas."
msgstr ""
"Korišćenje već georeferenciranih slojeva. To mogu biti vektorski ili "
"rasterski podaci koji sadrže iste objekte koje imate na slici koju želite da"
" georeferencirate i sa projekcijom koju želite za svoju sliku. U tom slučaju"
" možete uneti koordinate klikom na referentni skup podataka učitan u QGIS "
"platno karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:73
msgid ""
"The usual procedure for georeferencing an image involves selecting multiple "
"points on the raster, specifying their coordinates, and choosing a relevant "
"transformation type. Based on the input parameters and data, the "
"Georeferencer will compute the world file parameters. The more coordinates "
"you provide, the better the result will be."
msgstr ""
"Uobičajen postupak za georeferenciranje slike podrazumeva izbor više tačaka "
"na rasteru, zadavanje njihovih koordinata i izbor relevantnog tipa "
"transformacije. Na osnovu ulaznih parametara i podataka, Georeferencer će "
"izračunati parametre world datoteke. Što više koordinata pružite, to će "
"rezultat biti bolji."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:79
msgid ""
"The first step is to start QGIS and click on :menuselection:`Layer -->` "
"|georefRun| :menuselection:`Georeferencer`, which appears in the QGIS menu "
"bar. The Georeferencer dialog appears as shown in "
":numref:`figure_georeferencer_dialog`."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak je pokretanje QGIS-a i klik na :menuselection:`Sloj -->` "
"|georefRun| :menuselection:`Georeferencer`, koji se pojavljuje u traci "
"menija QGIS-a. Pojavljuje se dijalog Georeferencer kao što je prikazano na "
":numref:`figure_georeferencer_dialog`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:83
msgid ""
"For this example, we are using a topo sheet of South Dakota from SDGS. It "
"can later be visualized together with the data from the GRASS "
":file:`spearfish60` location. You can download the topo sheet here: "
"https://grass.osgeo.org/sampledata/spearfish_toposheet.tar.gz."
msgstr ""
"Za ovaj primer koristimo topografski list Južne Dakote iz SDGS-a. Kasnije se"
" može vizuelizovati zajedno sa podacima iz GRASS :file:`spearfish60` "
"lokacije. Topografski list možete preuzeti ovde: "
"https://grass.osgeo.org/sampledata/spearfish_toposheet.tar.gz."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:93
msgid "Georeferencer Dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog Georeferencer"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:99
msgid "Entering ground control points (GCPs)"
msgstr "Unos kontrolnih tačaka na terenu (GCP)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:101
msgid ""
"To start georeferencing an unreferenced raster, we must load it using the "
"|addRasterLayer| button. The raster will show up in the main working area of"
" the dialog. Once the raster is loaded, we can start to enter reference "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Da bismo počeli georeferenciranje nereferenciranog rastera, moramo ga "
"učitati pomoću dugmeta |addRasterLayer|. Raster će se pojaviti u glavnoj "
"radnoj oblasti dijaloga. Kada je raster učitan, možemo početi da unosimo "
"referentne tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:105
msgid ""
"Using the |addGCPPoint| :sup:`Add GCP Point` button, add points to the main "
"working area and enter their coordinates (see Figure "
":numref:`figure_georeferencer_add_points`). For this procedure you have the "
"following options:"
msgstr ""
"Pomoću dugmeta |addGCPPoint| :sup:`Dodaj GCP tačku` dodajte tačke u glavnu "
"radnu oblast i unesite njihove koordinate (pogledajte sliku "
":numref:`figure_georeferencer_add_points`). Za ovaj postupak imate sledeće "
"opcije:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:109
msgid ""
"Click on a point in the raster image and enter the X and Y coordinates "
"manually, along with the CRS of the point."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na tačku na rasterskoj slici i ručno unesite X i Y koordinate, "
"zajedno sa CRS-om tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:111
msgid ""
"Click on a point in the raster image and choose the |pencil| :sup:`From map "
"canvas` button to add the X and Y coordinates with the help of a "
"georeferenced map already loaded in the QGIS map canvas. The CRS will be set"
" automatically."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na tačku na rasterskoj slici i izaberite dugme |pencil| :sup:`Sa "
"platna karte` da biste dodali X i Y koordinate uz pomoć georeferencirane "
"karte već učitane u QGIS platno karte. CRS će biti postavljen automatski."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:403
msgid "pencil"
msgstr "pencil"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:115
msgid ""
"When entering GCPs from the main map canvas, you have the option to hide the"
" georeferencer window while selecting points from the main canvas. If the "
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Automatically hide georeferencer window` checkbox is "
"ticked, after clicking |pencil| :guilabel:`From Map Canvas`, the main "
"georeferencer window will be hidden until a point is added on the map "
"canvas. The :guilabel:`Enter Map Coordinates` dialog will remain open. If "
"the box is unchecked, both windows will remain open while selecting a point "
"on the map canvas. This option only takes effect when the georeferencer "
"window is not docked in the main interface."
msgstr ""
"Pri unosu GCP-ova sa glavnog platna karte, imate mogućnost da sakrijete "
"prozor georeferencer-a dok birate tačke sa glavnog platna. Ako je polje "
"|checkbox| :guilabel:`Automatski sakrij prozor georeferencer-a` označeno, "
"nakon klika na |pencil| :guilabel:`Sa platna karte`, glavni prozor "
"georeferencer-a biće sakriven dok se ne doda tačka na platnu karte. Dijalog "
":guilabel:`Unesite koordinate karte` ostaće otvoren. Ako polje nije "
"označeno, oba prozora ostaće otvorena dok birate tačku na platnu karte. Ova "
"opcija deluje samo kada prozor georeferencer-a nije usidren u glavnom "
"interfejsu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:381
msgid "checkbox"
msgstr "checkbox"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:126
msgid ""
"Continue entering points. You should have at least four points, and the more"
" coordinates you can provide, the better the result will be. There are "
"additional tools for zooming and panning the working area in order to locate"
" a relevant set of GCP points."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite sa unosom tačaka. Trebalo bi da imate bar četiri tačke, a što više"
" koordinata možete pružiti, to će rezultat biti bolji. Postoje dodatne "
"alatke za uveličavanje i pomeranje radne oblasti radi pronalaženja "
"relevantnog skupa GCP tačaka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:133
msgid ""
"To avoid constant switching between |pan| :sup:`Pan`, |addGCPPoint| "
":sup:`Add GCP point` and |moveGCPPoint| :sup:`Move GCP point` buttons, you "
"may use the keyboard arrow keys for moving and the mouse wheel for scaling "
"the georeferenced map conveniently."
msgstr ""
"Da biste izbegli stalno prebacivanje između dugmadi |pan| :sup:`Pomeri`, "
"|addGCPPoint| :sup:`Dodaj GCP tačku` i |moveGCPPoint| :sup:`Pomeri GCP "
"tačku`, možete zgodno koristiti strelice na tastaturi za pomeranje i točkić "
"miša za skaliranje georeferencirane karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:137
msgid ""
"After you provide a few points, you can use the |linkQGisToGeoref| "
":sup:`Link QGIS to Georeferencer` and/or |linkGeorefToQGis| :sup:`Link "
"Georeferencer to QGIS` buttons that will adjust, respectively, the map "
"extent of the main QGIS window to the present view in Georeferencer and/or "
"vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što pružite nekoliko tačaka, možete koristiti dugmad "
"|linkQGisToGeoref| :sup:`Poveži QGIS sa Georeferencer-om` i/ili "
"|linkGeorefToQGis| :sup:`Poveži Georeferencer sa QGIS-om` koja će "
"prilagoditi, redom, obuhvat karte glavnog QGIS prozora trenutnom prikazu u "
"Georeferencer-u i/ili obrnuto."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:140
msgid ""
"With the |moveGCPPoint| tool, you can move the GCPs in both the canvas and "
"the georeferencing window, if you need to correct them."
msgstr ""
"Alatkom |moveGCPPoint| možete pomerati GCP-ove i na platnu i u prozoru za "
"georeferenciranje, ako je potrebno da ih ispravite."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:148
msgid "Add points to the raster image"
msgstr "Dodavanje tačaka na rastersku sliku"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:150
msgid ""
"The points that are added to the map will be stored in a separate text file "
"(:file:`[filename].points`) usually together with the raster image. This "
"allows us to reopen the Georeferencer at a later date and add new points or "
"delete existing ones to optimize the result. The points file contains values"
" of the form: ``mapX, mapY, pixelX, pixelY``. You can use the "
"|loadGCPpoints| :sup:`Load GCP points` and |saveGCPPointsAs| :sup:`Save GCP "
"points as` buttons to manage the files."
msgstr ""
"Tačke koje se dodaju na kartu čuvaju se u zasebnoj tekstualnoj datoteci "
"(:file:`[filename].points`) obično zajedno sa rasterskom slikom. To nam "
"omogućava da ponovo otvorimo Georeferencer kasnije i dodamo nove tačke ili "
"obrišemo postojeće radi optimizacije rezultata. Datoteka tačaka sadrži "
"vrednosti oblika: ``mapX, mapY, pixelX, pixelY``. Za upravljanje datotekama "
"možete koristiti dugmad |loadGCPpoints| :sup:`Učitaj GCP tačke` i "
"|saveGCPPointsAs| :sup:`Sačuvaj GCP tačke kao`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:161
msgid "Defining the transformation settings"
msgstr "Definisanje podešavanja transformacije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:163
msgid ""
"After you have added your GCPs to the raster image, you need to define the "
"transformation settings for the georeferencing process."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što dodate GCP-ove na rastersku sliku, potrebno je da definišete "
"podešavanja transformacije za proces georeferenciranja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:171
msgid "Defining the georeferencer transformation settings"
msgstr "Definisanje podešavanja transformacije georeferencer-a"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:175
msgid "Available Transformation algorithms"
msgstr "Dostupni algoritmi transformacije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:177
msgid ""
"A number of transformation algorithms are available, dependent on the type "
"and quality of input data, the nature and amount of geometric distortion "
"that you are willing to introduce to the final result, and the number of "
"ground control points (GCPs)."
msgstr ""
"Dostupan je niz algoritama transformacije, u zavisnosti od tipa i kvaliteta "
"ulaznih podataka, prirode i količine geometrijske distorzije koju ste "
"spremni da unesete u konačni rezultat i broja kontrolnih tačaka na terenu "
"(GCP)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:181
msgid ""
"Currently, the following :guilabel:`Transformation types` are available:"
msgstr "Trenutno su dostupni sledeći :guilabel:`Tipovi transformacije`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:183
msgid ""
"The **Linear** algorithm is used to create a world file and is different "
"from the other algorithms, as it does not actually transform the raster "
"pixels. It allows positioning (translating) the image and uniform scaling, "
"but no rotation or other transformations. It is the most suitable if your "
"image is a good quality raster map, in a known CRS, but is just missing "
"georeferencing information. At least 2 GCPs are needed."
msgstr ""
"Algoritam **Linearni** koristi se za pravljenje world datoteke i razlikuje "
"se od drugih algoritama jer zapravo ne transformiše piksele rastera. "
"Omogućava pozicioniranje (translaciju) slike i jednoobrazno skaliranje, ali "
"ne i rotaciju ili druge transformacije. Najpogodniji je ako je vaša slika "
"rasterska karta dobrog kvaliteta, u poznatom CRS-u, ali joj samo nedostaju "
"informacije o georeferenciranju. Potrebne su najmanje 2 GCP tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:188
msgid ""
"The **Helmert** transformation also allows rotation. It is particularly "
"useful if your raster is a good quality local map or orthorectified aerial "
"image, but not aligned with the grid bearing in your CRS. At least 2 GCPs "
"are needed."
msgstr ""
"Transformacija **Helmert** takođe omogućava rotaciju. Naročito je korisna "
"ako je vaš raster lokalna karta dobrog kvaliteta ili ortorektifikovana "
"vazdušna slika, ali nije poravnata sa smerom mreže u vašem CRS-u. Potrebne "
"su najmanje 2 GCP tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:191
msgid ""
"The **Polynomial 1** algorithm allows a more general affine transformation, "
"in particular also a uniform shear. Straight lines remain straight (i.e., "
"collinear points stay collinear) and parallel lines remain parallel. This is"
" particularly useful for georeferencing data cartograms, which may have been"
" plotted (or data collected) with different ground pixel sizes in different "
"directions. At least 3 GCP's are required."
msgstr ""
"Algoritam **Polinomni 1** omogućava opštiju afinu transformaciju, naročito i"
" jednoobrazno smicanje. Prave linije ostaju prave (tj. kolinearne tačke "
"ostaju kolinearne), a paralelne linije ostaju paralelne. Ovo je naročito "
"korisno za georeferenciranje kartograma podataka, koji su možda iscrtani "
"(ili podaci prikupljeni) sa različitim veličinama piksela na terenu u "
"različitim pravcima. Potrebne su najmanje 3 GCP tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:195
msgid ""
"The **Polynomial** algorithms 2-3 use more general 2nd or 3rd degree "
"polynomials instead of just affine transformation. This allows them to "
"account for curvature or other systematic warping of the image, for instance"
" photographed maps with curving edges. At least 6 (respectively 10) GCP's "
"are required. Angles and local scale are not preserved or treated uniformly "
"across the image. In particular, straight lines may become curved, and there"
" may be significant distortion introduced at the edges or far from any GCPs "
"arising from extrapolating the data-fitted polynomials too far."
msgstr ""
"Algoritmi **Polinomni** 2-3 koriste opštije polinome 2. ili 3. stepena "
"umesto samo afine transformacije. To im omogućava da uzmu u obzir "
"zakrivljenost ili drugo sistematsko iskrivljenje slike, na primer "
"fotografisane karte sa zakrivljenim ivicama. Potrebno je najmanje 6 (odnosno"
" 10) GCP tačaka. Uglovi i lokalna razmera se ne čuvaju niti tretiraju "
"jednoobrazno preko slike. Naročito, prave linije mogu postati zakrivljene, a"
" na ivicama ili daleko od bilo kojih GCP-ova može doći do značajne "
"distorzije usled predalekog ekstrapoliranja polinoma prilagođenih podacima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:200
msgid ""
"The **Projective** algorithm generalizes Polynomial 1 in a different way, "
"allowing transformations representing a central projection between 2 non-"
"parallel planes, the image and the map canvas. Straight lines stay straight,"
" but parallelism is not preserved and scale across the image varies "
"consistently with the change in perspective. This transformation type is "
"most useful for georeferencing angled photographs (rather than flat scans) "
"of good quality maps, or oblique aerial images. A minimum of 4 GCPs is "
"required."
msgstr ""
"Algoritam **Projektivni** generalizuje Polinomni 1 na drugačiji način, "
"omogućavajući transformacije koje predstavljaju centralnu projekciju između "
"2 neparalelne ravni, slike i platna karte. Prave linije ostaju prave, ali se"
" paralelnost ne čuva, a razmera preko slike dosledno varira sa promenom "
"perspektive. Ovaj tip transformacije najkorisniji je za georeferenciranje "
"fotografija pod uglom (umesto ravnih skenova) karata dobrog kvaliteta, ili "
"kosih vazdušnih slika. Potrebne su najmanje 4 GCP tačke."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:205
msgid ""
"Finally, the **Thin Plate Spline** (TPS) algorithm \"rubber sheets\" the "
"raster using multiple local polynomials to match the GCPs specified, with "
"overall surface curvature minimized. Areas away from GCPs will be moved "
"around in the output to accommodate the GCP matching, but will otherwise be "
"minimally locally deformed.  TPS is most useful for georeferencing damaged, "
"deformed, or otherwise slightly inaccurate maps, or poorly orthorectified "
"aerials.  It is also useful for approximately georeferencing and implicitly "
"reprojecting maps with unknown projection type or parameters, but where a "
"regular grid or dense set of ad-hoc GCPs can be matched with a reference map"
" layer. It technically requires a minimum of 10 GCPs, but usually more to be"
" successful."
msgstr ""
"Najzad, algoritam **Thin Plate Spline** (TPS) „razvlači“ raster poput gume "
"koristeći više lokalnih polinoma za podudaranje sa zadatim GCP-ovima, uz "
"minimizovanu ukupnu zakrivljenost površine. Oblasti udaljene od GCP-ova biće"
" pomerene u izlazu radi prilagođavanja podudaranju GCP-ova, ali će inače "
"biti minimalno lokalno deformisane.  TPS je najkorisniji za "
"georeferenciranje oštećenih, deformisanih ili na drugi način blago netačnih "
"karata, ili loše ortorektifikovanih vazdušnih snimaka.  Koristan je i za "
"približno georeferenciranje i implicitno reprojektovanje karata sa "
"nepoznatim tipom ili parametrima projekcije, ali gde se pravilna mreža ili "
"gust skup ad-hoc GCP-ova može podudariti sa referentnim slojem karte. "
"Tehnički zahteva najmanje 10 GCP-ova, ali obično više da bi bio uspešan."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:212
msgid ""
"In all of the algorithms except TPS, if more than the minimum GCPs are "
"specified, parameters will be fitted so that the overall residual error is "
"minimized. This is helpful to minimize the impact of registration errors, "
"i.e. slight imprecisions in pointer clicks or typed coordinates, or other "
"small local image deformations. Absent other GCPs to compensate, such errors"
" or deformations could translate into significant distortions, especially "
"near the edges of the georeferenced image.  However, if more than the "
"minimum GCPs are specified, they will match only approximately in the "
"output. In contrast, TPS will precisely match all specified GCPs, but may "
"introduce significant deformations between nearby GCPs with registration "
"errors."
msgstr ""
"U svim algoritmima osim TPS-a, ako se zada više od minimalnog broja GCP-ova,"
" parametri će biti prilagođeni tako da se minimizuje ukupna rezidualna "
"greška. Ovo je korisno za minimizovanje uticaja grešaka registracije, tj. "
"blagih nepreciznosti u klikovima pokazivača ili unetim koordinatama, ili "
"drugih malih lokalnih deformacija slike. Bez drugih GCP-ova koji bi ih "
"kompenzovali, takve greške ili deformacije mogle bi se pretvoriti u značajne"
" distorzije, naročito blizu ivica georeferencirane slike.  Međutim, ako se "
"zada više od minimalnog broja GCP-ova, oni će se u izlazu podudarati samo "
"približno. Nasuprot tome, TPS će se precizno podudariti sa svim zadatim GCP-"
"ovima, ali može uneti značajne deformacije između bliskih GCP-ova sa "
"greškama registracije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:219
msgid "Define the Resampling method"
msgstr "Definisanje metoda preuzorkovanja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:221
msgid ""
"The type of resampling you choose will likely depend on your input data and "
"the ultimate objective of the exercise. If you don't want to change "
"statistics of the raster (other than as implied by nonuniform geometric "
"scaling if using other than the Linear, Helmert, or Polynomial 1 "
"transformations), you might want to choose 'Nearest neighbour'. In contrast,"
" 'cubic resampling', for instance, will usually generate a visually smoother"
" result."
msgstr ""
"Tip preuzorkovanja koji izaberete verovatno će zavisiti od vaših ulaznih "
"podataka i krajnjeg cilja vežbe. Ako ne želite da promenite statistiku "
"rastera (osim onako kako to podrazumeva neuniformno geometrijsko skaliranje "
"ako koristite nešto drugo osim Linearne, Helmert ili Polinomne 1 "
"transformacije), možda ćete želeti da izaberete „Najbliži sused“. Nasuprot "
"tome, „kubno preuzorkovanje“ će, na primer, obično dati vizuelno glađi "
"rezultat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:227
msgid "It is possible to choose between five different resampling methods:"
msgstr "Moguće je birati između pet različitih metoda preuzorkovanja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:229
msgid "Nearest neighbour"
msgstr "Najbliži sused"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:230
msgid "Bilinear (2x2 kernel)"
msgstr "Bilinearno (jezgro 2x2)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:231
msgid "Cubic (4x4 kernel)"
msgstr "Kubno (jezgro 4x4)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:232
msgid "Cubic B-Spline (4x4 kernel)"
msgstr "Kubni B-Spline (jezgro 4x4)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:233
msgid "Lanczos (6x6 kernel)"
msgstr "Lanczos (jezgro 6x6)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:236
msgid "Define the Raster creation options"
msgstr "Definisanje opcija pravljenja rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:238
msgid ""
"When exporting a raster, |checkbox| :guilabel:`Raster creation options` "
"allows you to define additional options that control how the output file is "
"structured and compressed. See more at :ref:`Raster driver options "
"<gdal_createoptions>`."
msgstr ""
"Pri izvozu rastera, |checkbox| :guilabel:`Opcije pravljenja rastera` "
"omogućava vam da definišete dodatne opcije koje kontrolišu kako je izlazna "
"datoteka strukturirana i komprimovana. Više pogledajte na :ref:`Opcije "
"rasterskog drajvera <gdal_createoptions>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:242
msgid ""
"Select an empty entry if you want to create your own custom combination of "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite prazan unos ako želite da napravite sopstvenu prilagođenu "
"kombinaciju parametara."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:245
msgid "Define the transformation settings"
msgstr "Definisanje podešavanja transformacije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:247
msgid ""
"There are several options that need to be defined for the georeferenced "
"output raster."
msgstr ""
"Postoji nekoliko opcija koje je potrebno definisati za georeferencirani "
"izlazni raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:250
msgid ""
"The |checkbox| :guilabel:`Create world file` checkbox is only available if "
"you decide to use the Linear or Helmert transformation type, because this "
"means that the raster image actually won't be transformed. In this case, the"
" :guilabel:`Output raster` field is not activated, because only a new world "
"file will be created."
msgstr ""
"Polje |checkbox| :guilabel:`Napravi world datoteku` dostupno je samo ako "
"odlučite da koristite tip transformacije Linearni ili Helmert, jer to znači "
"da rasterska slika zapravo neće biti transformisana. U tom slučaju polje "
":guilabel:`Izlazni raster` nije aktivirano, jer će biti napravljena samo "
"nova world datoteka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:255
msgid ""
"For all other transformation types, you have to define an :guilabel:`Output "
"raster`. As default, a new file ([filename]_modified) will be created in the"
" same folder together with the original raster image."
msgstr ""
"Za sve druge tipove transformacije, morate definisati :guilabel:`Izlazni "
"raster`. Podrazumevano se nova datoteka ([filename]_modified) pravi u istom "
"folderu zajedno sa originalnom rasterskom slikom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:258
msgid ""
"As a next step, you have to define the :guilabel:`Target CRS` (Coordinate "
"Reference System) for the georeferenced raster (see "
":ref:`label_projections`)."
msgstr ""
"Kao sledeći korak, morate definisati :guilabel:`Ciljni CRS` (koordinatni "
"referentni sistem) za georeferencirani raster (pogledajte "
":ref:`label_projections`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:260
msgid ""
"If you like, you can **generate a pdf map** and also **a pdf report**. The "
"report includes information about the used transformation parameters, an "
"image of the residuals and a list with all GCPs and their RMS errors."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite, možete **generisati pdf kartu** i takođe **pdf izveštaj**. "
"Izveštaj uključuje informacije o korišćenim parametrima transformacije, "
"sliku reziduala i listu sa svim GCP-ovima i njihovim RMS greškama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:263
msgid ""
"Furthermore, you can activate the |checkbox| :guilabel:`Set Target "
"Resolution` checkbox and define the pixel resolution of the output raster. "
"Default horizontal and vertical resolution is 1."
msgstr ""
"Osim toga, možete aktivirati polje |checkbox| :guilabel:`Postavi ciljnu "
"rezoluciju` i definisati rezoluciju piksela izlaznog rastera. Podrazumevana "
"horizontalna i vertikalna rezolucija je 1."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:266
msgid ""
"The |checkbox| :guilabel:`Use 0 for transparency when needed` can be "
"activated, if pixels with the value 0 shall be visualized transparent. In "
"our example toposheet, all white areas would be transparent."
msgstr ""
"Polje |checkbox| :guilabel:`Koristi 0 za prozirnost kada je potrebno` može "
"se aktivirati ako pikseli sa vrednošću 0 treba da budu vizuelizovani "
"prozirno. U našem primeru topografskog lista, sve bele oblasti bile bi "
"prozirne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:269
msgid ""
"The |checkbox| :guilabel:`Save GCP Points` will store GCP Points in a file "
"next to the output raster."
msgstr ""
"Polje |checkbox| :guilabel:`Sačuvaj GCP tačke` čuvaće GCP tačke u datoteci "
"pored izlaznog rastera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:271
msgid ""
"Finally, |checkbox| :guilabel:`Load in project when done` loads the output "
"raster automatically into the QGIS map canvas when the transformation is "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Najzad, |checkbox| :guilabel:`Učitaj u projekat po završetku` automatski "
"učitava izlazni raster u QGIS platno karte kada je transformacija završena."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:278
msgid "Running the transformation"
msgstr "Pokretanje transformacije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:280
msgid ""
"After all GCPs have been collected and all transformation settings are "
"defined, just press the |start| :sup:`Start georeferencing` button to create"
" the new georeferenced raster."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što su svi GCP-ovi prikupljeni i sva podešavanja transformacije "
"definisana, samo pritisnite dugme |start| :sup:`Pokreni georeferenciranje` "
"da biste napravili novi georeferencirani raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:286
msgid "Georeferencing vector layer"
msgstr "Georeferenciranje vektorskog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:288
msgid ""
"Georeferencing vector layers works similarly to raster georeferencing, but "
"instead of matching image pixels, you match vector geometries (points, "
"lines, or polygons) to known spatial references."
msgstr ""
"Georeferenciranje vektorskih slojeva radi slično georeferenciranju rastera, "
"ali umesto podudaranja piksela slike, podudarate vektorske geometrije "
"(tačke, linije ili poligone) sa poznatim prostornim referencama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:291
msgid ""
"The standard procedure starts the same as for raster georeferencing: open "
"QGIS and add a layer to the map canvas to use as a reference. This can be a "
"georeferenced raster or vector layer, or a WMS layer."
msgstr ""
"Standardni postupak počinje isto kao za georeferenciranje rastera: otvorite "
"QGIS i dodajte sloj na platno karte da biste ga koristili kao referencu. To "
"može biti georeferencirani rasterski ili vektorski sloj, ili WMS sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:295
msgid ""
"Open the Georeferencer dialog from :menuselection:`Layer -->` |georefRun| "
":menuselection:`Georeferencer`."
msgstr ""
"Otvorite dijalog Georeferencer iz :menuselection:`Sloj -->` |georefRun| "
":menuselection:`Georeferencer`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:297
msgid ""
"Start georeferencing by following these steps (in this example, we use an "
"unreferenced ``alaska.shp``):"
msgstr ""
"Pokrenite georeferenciranje prateći ove korake (u ovom primeru koristimo "
"nereferencirani ``alaska.shp``):"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:304
msgid "Vector Georeferencer Dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog Vektorski georeferencer"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:306
msgid ""
"Load the unreferenced vector layer using the |addOgrLayer| button. The "
"vector layer will appear in the main working area of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Učitajte nereferencirani vektorski sloj pomoću dugmeta |addOgrLayer|. "
"Vektorski sloj će se pojaviti u glavnoj radnoj oblasti dijaloga."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:309
msgid ""
"Activate snapping by clicking the |snapping| button and selecting the "
"desired snapping type(s). This enables snapping to the reference layer when "
"placing GCPs."
msgstr ""
"Aktivirajte lepljenje klikom na dugme |snapping| i izborom željenog "
"tipa(ova) lepljenja. Time se omogućava lepljenje za referentni sloj pri "
"postavljanju GCP-ova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:312
msgid ""
"You can also use the |cad| :sup:`Advanced Digitizing` dock to ensure high-"
"precision point selection. For more information, refer to the :ref:`Advanced"
" Digitizing <advanced_digitizing_panel>` section."
msgstr ""
"Takođe možete koristiti dok |cad| :sup:`Napredno digitalizovanje` da biste "
"obezbedili izbor tačaka visoke preciznosti. Za više informacija pogledajte "
"odeljak :ref:`Napredno digitalizovanje <advanced_digitizing_panel>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:316
msgid ""
"Use the |addGCPPoint| :sup:`Add GCP Point` button to add a point to the "
"working area. Enter its coordinates manually and set the CRS, or click the "
"|pencil| :sup:`From map canvas` button to pick the coordinates from a "
"georeferenced layer in the main QGIS map canvas. In that case, the CRS will "
"be set automatically."
msgstr ""
"Koristite dugme |addGCPPoint| :sup:`Dodaj GCP tačku` da biste dodali tačku u"
" radnu oblast. Ručno unesite njene koordinate i postavite CRS, ili kliknite "
"na dugme |pencil| :sup:`Sa platna karte` da biste izabrali koordinate iz "
"georeferenciranog sloja na glavnom QGIS platnu karte. U tom slučaju CRS će "
"biti postavljen automatski."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:321
msgid "Define the transformation settings:"
msgstr "Definišite podešavanja transformacije:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:323
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Transformation type`. The transformation algorithms "
"are the same as those for raster georeferencing. See "
":ref:`georeferencer_transformation` for more details."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite :guilabel:`Tip transformacije`. Algoritmi transformacije su isti "
"kao oni za georeferenciranje rastera. Za više detalja pogledajte "
":ref:`georeferencer_transformation`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:326
msgid ""
"Define the :guilabel:`Target CRS` (Coordinate Reference System) for the "
"georeferenced vector (see :ref:`label_projections`)."
msgstr ""
"Definišite :guilabel:`Ciljni CRS` (koordinatni referentni sistem) za "
"georeferencirani vektor (pogledajte :ref:`label_projections`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:328
msgid ""
"Set the output file format and path (e.g., GeoPackage, Shapefile). By "
"default, a new file with suffix ``_modified`` will be created in the same "
"folder as the original vector file."
msgstr ""
"Postavite format i putanju izlazne datoteke (npr. GeoPackage, Shapefile). "
"Podrazumevano se nova datoteka sa sufiksom ``_modified`` pravi u istom "
"folderu kao originalna vektorska datoteka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:331
msgid ""
"Optionally, enable **Generate PDF map** and **Generate PDF report**. The "
"report includes transformation parameters, GCP residuals, and a summary of "
"RMS errors."
msgstr ""
"Opciono, omogućite **Generiši PDF kartu** i **Generiši PDF izveštaj**. "
"Izveštaj uključuje parametre transformacije, GCP reziduale i rezime RMS "
"grešaka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:333
msgid ""
"Enable |checkbox| :guilabel:`Save GCP Points` to store GCPs in a file "
"alongside the output vector layer."
msgstr ""
"Omogućite |checkbox| :guilabel:`Sačuvaj GCP tačke` da biste sačuvali GCP-ove"
" u datoteci uz izlazni vektorski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:334
msgid ""
"Enable |checkbox| :guilabel:`Load in project when done` to add the result "
"directly to the map canvas."
msgstr ""
"Omogućite |checkbox| :guilabel:`Učitaj u projekat po završetku` da biste "
"dodali rezultat direktno na platno karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:336
msgid ""
"Click |start| :sup:`Start georeferencing` to run the transformation and "
"generate the georeferenced vector layer."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na |start| :sup:`Pokreni georeferenciranje` da biste pokrenuli "
"transformaciju i generisali georeferencirani vektorski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:339
msgid "Show and adapt layer properties"
msgstr "Prikaz i prilagođavanje svojstava sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:341
msgid ""
"Clicking on the :guilabel:`Source properties` option in the "
":guilabel:`Settings` menu opens the :ref:`Raster Layer properties "
"<raster_properties_dialog>` or :ref:`Vector Layer properties "
"<vector_properties_dialog>` depending on the type of layer you are "
"georeferencing."
msgstr ""
"Klik na opciju :guilabel:`Svojstva izvora` u meniju :guilabel:`Podešavanja` "
"otvara :ref:`Svojstva rasterskog sloja <raster_properties_dialog>` ili "
":ref:`Svojstva vektorskog sloja <vector_properties_dialog>` u zavisnosti od "
"tipa sloja koji georeferencirate."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:349
msgid "Configure the georeferencer"
msgstr "Konfigurisanje georeferencer-a"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:351
msgid ""
"You can customize the behavior of the georeferencer in "
":menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Georeferencer` (or use keyboard "
"shortcut :kbd:`Ctrl+P`)."
msgstr ""
"Ponašanje georeferencer-a možete prilagoditi u :menuselection:`Podešavanja "
"--> Konfiguriši Georeferencer` (ili koristite prečicu na tastaturi "
":kbd:`Ctrl+P`)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:354
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Point Tip` you can use the checkboxes to toggle displaying "
"GCP IDs and X/Y coordinates in both the Georeferencer window and the main "
"map canvas."
msgstr ""
"Pod :guilabel:`Savet za tačku` možete koristiti polja za potvrdu da biste "
"uključili/isključili prikaz GCP ID-jeva i X/Y koordinata i u prozoru "
"Georeferencer-a i na glavnom platnu karte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:356
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Residual Units` controls whether residual units are given in "
"pixels or map units"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jedinice reziduala` kontroliše da li se jedinice reziduala daju u"
" pikselima ili jedinicama karte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:358
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PDF Report` allows you to set margin size in mm for the report "
"export"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PDF izveštaj` omogućava vam da postavite veličinu margine u mm za"
" izvoz izveštaja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:359
msgid ""
":guilabel:`PDF Map` allows you to choose a paper size for the map export"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`PDF karta` omogućava vam da izaberete veličinu papira za izvoz "
"karte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/managing_data_source/georeferencer.rst:360
msgid ""
"Finally, you can activate to |checkbox| :guilabel:`Show Georeferencer window"
" docked`. This will dock the Georeferencer window in the main QGIS window "
"rather than showing it as a separate window that can be minimized."
msgstr ""
"Najzad, možete aktivirati |checkbox| :guilabel:`Prikaži prozor "
"Georeferencer-a usidren`. Time se prozor Georeferencer-a usidruje u glavni "
"QGIS prozor umesto da se prikazuje kao zaseban prozor koji se može "
"minimizovati."
